Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.99,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(397,517)\pos(1442,852.667)}前往与祖父大人共住的楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,红茶是非常精致的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:51.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,注入开水之后  要盖上盖子慢慢浸泡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,关键是不能急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,揭开盖子  用勺子轻轻搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:59.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,用漏勺过滤后倒入杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:06.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,然后品一下茶香  再尝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这就是大人的喝法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你口渴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,给你喝加了很多糖的红茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不过  你要先回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:27.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你的主人是叛乱分子  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特究竟在谋划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我没有什么可以说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没有凯特小姐的许可我是什么都不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,威…威胁我也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只是一段时间不能喝水而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要是那个时候把面包吃完就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是个毫无紧张感的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:06.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,时间还很多  我要在早上之前挖出所有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,送到伟大的祖父大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华是在祖父大人那栋对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说我们得潜入那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那种事情真的能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你再稍微认真想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那乔恩你来想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我一下子也想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你有什么主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你总是沉着冷静  会观察周围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可是这么跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,请你帮帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:49.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没错吧  尚恩确实是很聪明  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了  请给我点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:57.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:04:02.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样才能不被发现地去到祖父大人那栋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,况且情报也太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,完全不知道那栋宅邸是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可能还会设有什么陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:17.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,连通祖父大人那栋的路我就只知道那条走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:21.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是入口有无面人偶在看守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:23.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:31.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了  唯一一个成功的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在吃面包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不过你还能靠妄想撑到到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没关系  我已经饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:05:00.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要你告诉我凯特在谋划的事情  给你松绑也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那就继续绑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这我也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那你就把凯特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你知道现在是什么情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:18.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,吃饱之后我就犯困了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那我们来聊点开心的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:25.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,其实你也不乐意做这种事的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我不会说有关凯特小姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是你的事情不管多少我都会听的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们来聊各种话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那样绝对很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:50.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,别急啊爱德华  这不是什么难事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们要从这个走廊堂堂正正地前往对面的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,伪装成无面人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:03.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  爱德华也是这样过来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不愧是尚恩  注意到了关键
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您过奖了  乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:12.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那乔恩也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:16.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,人数越多  被发现的风险也越高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是我们不是不知道埃米莉可在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,分头去找比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  我们没有互相联络的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:31.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不过  一个人去那间宅邸找人也太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在书里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:38.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,祖父大人那一栋  楼层越高住的人身份越高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一楼  二楼  三楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你们觉得爱德华会住在哪一楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,话说像他那样的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要用诱拐这样鬼鬼祟祟的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,鬼鬼祟祟…确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么他要冒这种风险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:07:01.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我说  还要偷无面人偶的制服吧  你打算怎么偷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:05.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,对  肯定有个地方放着替换用的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这个时间会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:14.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克  马上开门  你在吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那个戴星的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不好了  声音被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,从利奇的房间逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是活人偶的房间在外面上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一旦有情况就用乔恩拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不可以  门坏掉的话  帕利克少爷会被怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你打算让我等到什么时候  快点开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没有思考的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:43.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,总之这里就交给帕利克和利奇吧  大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  就那样办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉  深更半夜的有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:59.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,刚才从这房间里传出了好几个人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,作为戴星组  我要进行室内搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你那是误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是误会的话  检查一下也不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭比  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  锁住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没办法了  把门破坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等  我们有麻烦了  过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,巡逻辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在和谁讲话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好了  我们逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:53.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝的黑灰可以控制活人偶啊  你们已经忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这里没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:02.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,最后只剩活人偶的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这之后要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,首先要弄到制服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那继续控制她给我们带路就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:27.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没错  凯特和露薏丝一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那乔恩我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们去看下对面楼那边的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,说不定能发现潜入的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也对  我们在那个走廊前集合吧  凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  千万不要被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:50.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都怪我一不小心和利奇聊得太热烈了  我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那个  你之前有巡逻过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华成为儿童楼的管理员之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:03.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要求我们包括小纠纷在内的所有问题都要报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爱德华？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他在「露面」中被表扬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是呢  但事无巨细都要报告吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是因为他很渴望出人头地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,令人火大的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:19.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,芭芭拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:26.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这之后少做些可疑的举动  帕利克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:28.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,刚才的情报能用来救埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:48.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:51.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要为了那样的活人偶做到这个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才不是「那样的活人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她是埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,还有  你是利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.84,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这  肯定会有守卫的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到关键时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能用乔恩拳  要是他们呼叫救援怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,仔细一看  离得相当远啊  悬崖还很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这么黑也看不太清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:30.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们去过的就只有「露面」的那一层
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,现在就只能将看得见的外观和记忆中的对照起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:37.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想象宅邸的内部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那露薏丝就陪你到这了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不想继续以身犯险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之后你就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了  真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:04.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我只是想炫耀自己的黑灰能力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这对露薏丝来说是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:09.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  麻烦祝我成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏丝小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,虽然这次他盯上的碰巧是凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但之后说不定会轮到露薏丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就是说  他也许会抢走露对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让他对露出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌爱德华了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,糟了  被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等  我是凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.66,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们这栋的一楼与对面的地下一层相连对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:57.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,穿过走廊之后  请您去找楼梯往上走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我猜对面的栋也会有人偶巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但既然扮作「看不见脸的人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算被发现应该也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:09.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是要上到三楼  再怎么说也有点难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不  没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克和利奇  你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:20.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,听芭芭拉说  爱德华是儿童栋的管理人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他想更出人头地上到三楼去  也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他住在二楼或一楼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:29.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但房间的数量也很多  不可能一间间去查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,交给凯特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可别失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:41.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  一定会两个人一起回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:51.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为我很担心啊  乔恩替你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你帮我到这里就已经足够了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她好像成功进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克我们也该回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:58.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,被巡逻的发现就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们也回去吧  乔恩少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:07.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,这难道是装咖啡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看来是在这里制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都是正常的瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然是在泡完咖啡之后加了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:08.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我这样做也是为了凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想在无法挽回之前拯救她  所以需要你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:15.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再这样下去凯特会被处置的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:19.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因为你毫无用处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,正因为有像你这样的废物  凯特才不会向往高处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:32.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,所以她才会想要背叛影宅  这跟小孩子闹脾气是一个道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只是在泄愤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:36.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,请不要说凯特小姐的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你心里没点数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:43.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你总是想多余的事  无视规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:50.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你不觉得是不守影宅规矩的你引导凯特走错路的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,听着  现在我给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:02.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要你全都招认  我就会救凯特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,现在能救凯特的就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:09.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快说吧  凯特在谋划着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大箱子？难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小面包  在的话就动一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告诉我你在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再试一次  更用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:52.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我要专心寻找埃米莉可才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小面包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,面包？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:12.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快  回答我  凯特在谋划着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比任何人都勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比任何人都温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她是我最重要的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:34.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地板都被你弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,给我安静待着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,难道是用来拐走埃米莉可的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你没事吧  我在外面听到了什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你还真的把她抓来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去外面说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:32.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,刚才应该是小面包撞倒杯子落地的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐为了让我恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哭着让我喝下了水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:47.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,把我看做一个独立的人  叫我埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:52.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,总是温柔地守护着冒失的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:03.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,很好  没有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不能慌了神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:36.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想去确认爱德华说有侵入者的事情是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想救那个活人偶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她就会模仿爱德华变装成「看不见脸的人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,到时候应该会推着推车过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,总不可能把推车搬到二楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只要数一下地下一层的推车数量就知道她有没有来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:07.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,糟了  得在那两个人回来之前救出埃米莉可才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:14.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小面包  你在的话就给点反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:19.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,告诉我埃米莉可的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:21.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:30.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在这里  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:34.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哪里  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你还好吗  我现在帮你解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我们现在快离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不是的  凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:56.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
